        "reaction_type_english": "Cracking reaction",
        "description": "在高压反应器中，使用Fe/SiO₂–Al₂O₃固体酸催化剂，在无溶剂条件下对模型底物甲基油酸酯以及各种油（亚麻籽油、菜籽油、印楝油和桐油）进行加氢处理，以生产生物航煤级烷烃（C8至C15）。优化条件为：380°C，5 bar H₂压力，10%铁负载量，反应5小时，实现了100%转化率和>74%的选择性。",
        "text_snippet": "The hydrotreatment experiments were conducted in a high-pressure reactor to optimize the reaction conditions, such as operating temperature, reaction time, H₂ pressure, and catalyst loading... The investigation demonstrates ∼100% conversion with >74% hydrocracking selectivity at 5 bar pressure in 5 h under solvent-free conditions.",
